  "texts": [
    "Suppose, for example, that one initially regards a given piece of video footage as authentic.",
    "Suppose that footage is flagged as fake by an ADD.",
    "Even if one does not defer to the detector, one might nonetheless think that the system's judgment is a sufficient reason to scrutinize the video more carefully.",
    "3 In this way, ADDs might serve to prompt more careful consideration of evidence by humans.",
    "Additionally, over time, comparing one's judgments to that of ADDs may help one to develop one's own discriminatory abilities."
  ],
